n the West Java Province region.</span></li></ol>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div style=" color: rgb(0, 204, 255); font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; text-align: justify"><a href="https://kearsipan.undip.ac.id/download/" target="_blank" style=" color: rgb(0, 204, 255); text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.2s; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold">Download Law no. 43 of 2009 concerning Archives and Government Regulation no. 28 of 2012 concerning Implementation.</a></div>', 'tugas_fungsi', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '["features/profile/DQ68brYAeP2f7qAYnGLIStKuVn3OHJEqRZ8EtvU0.png", "features/profile/P8PpSNocGdLWyAA9RY6DnQpCaheZOYYx8TNWBg3n.png"]', '[{"width": "128", "height": "121", "offsetX": "170", "offsetY": "22", "position": "51.79% 46.06%"}, {"width": "167", "height": "156", "offsetX": "207", "offsetY": "194", "position": "50% 50%"}]', 1, '2026-04-15 19:59:42', '2026-04-20 20:44:57');
